features: SEAMLESS LOOK: Elegantly dress up your microwave with this stainless steel Panasonic 30 Inch 1.6 Cubic Foot Microwave Oven Trim Kit
SPECIFIC MEASUREMENTS: Designed to fit with inner dimensions of 22.63 inches long by 11.63 inches tall, and outer dimensions of 30 inches long, 0.75 inches wide, and 16.5 inches tall
COMPATIBLE WITH MULTIPLE MODELS: Built for compatibility with model NN-TK732SS, NN-SE782S, NN-SD797S, and NN-SD762S microwaves; ensure the model fits before purchase
BASIC INSTALLATION: Requires basic and minimal technical skill for proper installation, needing only a drill or screwdriver
FULL ENCASING: Includes trim frame, an upper, lower, and rear duct meant for attaching to encase your microwave oven in the cut-out opening
body.description: Before heading to purchase a brand new built-in microwave oven model, consider converting your Panasonic microwave into an encased version with the certified refurbished Panasonic NN-TK732SS 30 Inch, 1.6 Cubic Foot Microwave Trim Kit. Certain microwave appliance models are also compatible with the trim kit including NN-SE782S, NN-SD797S, and NN-SD762S. A trim kit for your microwave has the opportunity to save you additional countertop space while cooking up your favorite meals in a tasteful fashion. The sleek, stainless steel design pairs well with select Panasonic microwaves with inner dimensions of 22.63 inches long by 11.63 inches tall. Because this stainless steel oven trim kit comes with a trim frame, an upper, lower, and read duct, simply find a space between your cabinets that fits the outer dimensions of the kit: 30 inches long, 0.75 inches wide, and 16.5 inches tall. Whether you enjoy the installation process or not, the task of transforming your microwave oven is minimalistic. Grab a Phillips head screwdriver or a drill and get to work on upgrading your space.
